{"tid":972112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女友抱肌萎男去殘廁 要放佢喺「尿液地板」極唔衞生","createTime":"2019-01-07T07:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T07:59:07.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0d03ea9dbb9ec078ce5cb6ad8dba6b9f093b094b","tid":972112,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190106/large/1546751903_5d52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190106%2Flarge%2F1546751903_5d52.jpg&h=5253ffd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190106/large/1546762375_7391.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190106%2Flarge%2F1546762375_7391.jpg&h=e139c8a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少公共地方都設有殘疾人士洗手間，但其設計卻未必能夠體貼用家的需要。美國一名患上脊髓肌肉萎縮症的男子，早前與女友到訪英國，他們在使用殘廁時遇到重重障礙，由於馬桶太大，加上洗手間內沒有尿布檯，他「要躺在佈滿尿液的濕地板上」使用尿壺，他特意拍片希望引起關注改善問題。<br />\n<br />\n患有脊髓肌肉萎縮症（Spinal Muscular Atrophy）的伯考（Shane Burcaw）來自美國明尼阿波利斯市，他平日要用輪椅代步，出遠門時要使用尿壺。最近他與女友艾爾沃德（Hannah Aylward）到英國倫敦，在聖潘克拉斯國際火車站使用殘廁時發現，洗手間內的設計不能便利殘疾人士。<br />\n<br />\n片中艾爾沃德抱起伯考，嘗試放他上馬桶，但因為馬桶太大，無論從哪個方向，都無法讓伯考坐穩，最後艾爾沃德示範要將伯考放在地上，讓他完全躺下。「因為沒有尿布檯，也因為馬桶太大，我要躺在地上，不幸的是，地上滿佈尿液和其他不明液體。」伯考嘆道︰「噢，濕漉漉的，有些濕漉漉，天啊，我躺在有尿液的地上」，艾爾沃德也說︰「地上全是濕的，有廁紙沾到我腳上了。」<br />\n<br />\n他們表示，殘疾人士洗手間須增設尿布檯，「這不只是我的問題，是所有殘疾、或帶着孩子的健全人士也面對的問題，我們都需要尿布檯。」<br />\n<br />\n伯考和健全的艾爾沃德已經拍拖三年，他們在6個月前開始拍片分享不平凡愛情的日常生活，希望讓大眾對殘疾人士有更多了解，消除社會上的歧視。"},{"pid":"a47435308a1d3adf8245ce443619a25c24536f09","tid":972112,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:18:56.000Z","msg":"無得放低個馬桶蓋<br />\n坐喺上面用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d30dfaa7f8ae70d95b400266ade1379eadc3d5d","tid":972112,"uid":122134,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:19:06.000Z","msg":"咁都有....."},{"pid":"49cf46ae8238b92f7c4c67b759483c853842a2f9","tid":972112,"uid":49197,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:20:27.000Z","msg":"肌肉萎縮都有正常樣女友...頂..."},{"pid":"dace0ade4867d01782ff78546ac31bbe470a9632","tid":972112,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:21:00.000Z","msg":"搵野墊一墊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa05f739f2789c46ae2d8bc1b365d7957d54fda","tid":972112,"uid":161190,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:42:24.000Z","msg":"屌 有無搞撚錯<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/07/154212_8ba449983deea393749fa816f9ee2403.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F07%2F154212_8ba449983deea393749fa816f9ee2403.png&h=f6ed71bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8579f7550576648e034bb7aac6a0f65383635a36","tid":972112,"uid":65774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:47:54.000Z","msg":"肌肉委縮都有閪屌，毒撚真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2723bfe5df8871e90750525a78511b515ca813","tid":972112,"uid":190383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49cf46ae8238b92f7c4c67b759483c853842a2f9","tid":972112,"uid":49197,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:20:27.000Z","msg":"肌肉萎縮都有正常樣女友...頂..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:49:16.000Z","msg":"條女有糧出嫁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能"},{"pid":"6df3e80bd94ad2bb63293f67ff6b3608d942655c","tid":972112,"uid":167330,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:51:35.000Z","msg":"連登仔連肌痿男都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d40be43c486d96a9fd3d2f15630641713b9b5c","tid":972112,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bd2723bfe5df8871e90750525a78511b515ca813","tid":972112,"uid":190383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49c